description.en:
Interline Eco filter set

This Interline filter set is a low-cost filter set suitable for small and medium sized pools. The minimum pump capacity is 6 m³/hour. The air valve of the pump can be filled with fiberclean, so you always keep your pool clean.

Specifications:
Colour: white
Gender: unisex
Material: plastic
Length of hose: 2x 4.5 metres
Pumping power: 450 watts
Voltage: 230V
Minimum pump capacity: 6 m³/hour
Pool capacity: 20.000 to 30.000 liters
Maximum working pressure: 0.4 bar
Weight: 11.5 kg

Contents:
2 hoses
4 Hose clamps
1 RCD plug
1 Set fiberclean
